description: It’s the holidays and these two wanted to do something a little more fun than just a quick interview. Surprisingly it was the quiet Tate that suggested an idea. “Lets do something to get in the holiday spirit, you know, really bring some damn holiday cheer to SeanCody." So we packed up the car and went off to buy the fixings to make some gingerbread houses. “I have a feeling this is going to get messy!” Forrest laughed. It was fun watching these two attempt to make some holiday décor. Lets just say they are much better at fucking. When it came time to get down to business, Forrest and Tate hit it out of the park and really nailed a great film.
title: Tate & Forrest: Bareback
